Ok.  I didn't see an example to follow.  Looking around, I see how mountoptions are handled now.  Do you want us to similarly add an extra options argument at the end of chown, ala:
chown <owner> <group> <path> [ <chownoption> ]*
<chownoption>s include "recurse"

